<paragraph id="IFRS01_BC74"><paranum>BC74</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="BC74"/></prolog><body><variant id="IFRS01_BC74_V2" base="F19755429" principles="no"> <p id="IFRS01_P2852">The Board considered practical implementation difficulties that could arise from the retrospective application of aspects of IAS 39:<xref keyref="footnotes/IFRS01_FN0036" type="fn"/> </p> <ol id="IFRS01_L0156" base="F19755431" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS01_P2853" base="F19755433">hedge accounting (<xref id="IFRS01_X1795" base="F19755434" href="IFRS01_gBC75-BC80.dita#IFRS01_gBC75-BC80">paragraphs BC75&#x2013;BC80</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS01_P2854" base="F22303360">government loans (paragraphs BC80A&#x2013;BC80E);</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS01_P2855" base="F19755436">the treatment of cumulative fair value changes on available&#x2011;for&#x2011;sale financial assets<xref keyref="footnotes/IFRS01_FN0037" type="fn"/> at the date of transition to IFRSs (<xref id="IFRS01_X1796" base="F19755438" href="IFRS01_gBC81-BC83A.dita#IFRS01_gBC81-BC83A">paragraphs BC81&#x2013;BC83</xref>); and</p></li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value> <p id="IFRS01_P2856" base="F19755440">&#x2018;day 1&#x2019; gain or loss recognition (<xref id="IFRS01_X1797" base="F19755441" href="IFRS01_BC83A.dita#IFRS01_BC83A">paragraph BC83A</xref>).</p></li></ol></variant></body></paragraph>